refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
ImagickPixel
arraygetHSL
&warn.undocumented.func;
Returns the normalized HSL color described by the ImagickPixel object, with each of the three values as floating point numbers between 0.0 and 1.0.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns the HSL value in an array with the keys "hue",
 "saturation", and "luminosity". Throws ImagickPixelException on failure.
